description:
This vegan Calamari is made of king trumpet mushroom coated in batter and deep-fried until crispy on the outside and chewy on the inside. It's perfect as appetizer, snack, beer pairing, or party food. Kain na, let's eat! Full recipe: http://www.astigvegan.com/vegan-calamari-2
